        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/8e8cbc/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2023-10-01T13:22:14.833Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The labels were in pretty good shape, but I\u2019m with you in that humidity stained labels are generally a neutral to positive indicator.   I had been mostly worried that \u201csubterranean\u201d, when used alone, meant basement that wasn\u2019t otherwise climate controlled.   However and wherever they were stored seems to have been fine, though, based on the wines I\u2019ve opened.</p>",
